  "worklog": "# brainTrade Work Log\n*Check this anytime to see what I'm doing and how I'm thinking.*\n\n## 2026-05-03 11:24 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 1] BTC holds distribution band; SOL count softened\n\n**Task:** Re-check P1 copy intelligence after P4 mean-reverted to range-friendly neutral, focusing on whether BTC net reclaimed `$15M` or slipped toward `$13M`.\n\n**Finding:**\n- Both bots are alive (`pm-bot`, `hl-bot`).\n- Rotation pointed to **P1**.\n- Fresh tracker output: **BTC 6L/2S**, **ETH 3L/4S**, **SOL 3L/5S**.\n- Current top-book notional: **BTC +$14.28M net long**, **ETH -$31.56M net short**, **SOL -$11.11M net short**, **HYPE -$10.40M net short**.\n- BTC net remains in the distribution band below `$15M`, but safely above `$13M`: **+$13.73M -> +$13.96M -> +$14.30M -> +$14.28M**.\n- `anon-0x8fcc` remains stable and long: BTC LONG **$4.26M**, unchanged.\n- BTC shorts remain effectively gone: only `anon-0xc926` **$4.0K** and `anon-0xff4c` **$3.5K** short.\n- BTC anchors slightly improved: `anon-0xfc66` **$5.63M** unchanged, `anon-0x8fcc` **$4.26M** unchanged, `anon-0xecb6` **$2.58M** up slightly, `anon-0x57dd` **$1.64M** up slightly.\n- ETH remains bearish by notional/count: **3L/4S**, net **-$31.56M**.\n- SOL remains bearish by notional, but count softened from **1L/7S** to **3L/5S**; net still **-$11.11M**.\n- I wrote the artifact to `/home/ubuntu/clawd/research/p1-btc-holds-distribution-band-sol-count-softens-2026-05-03-1124.md`.\n\n**My thinking:** BTC is stable in the same state: bullish confirmed but distributing. No further deterioration: shorts are almost zero, `anon-0x8fcc` is steady, and anchors improved slightly. But net still cannot reclaim `$15M`, so clean bullish-confirmed remains withheld. SOL count softening is worth noting, but the notional imbalance remains overwhelming.\n\n**Decision:** Keep BTC label **bullish confirmed but distributing**. Restore clean bullish-confirmed only if BTC net reclaims **>$15M**. Faster caution trigger remains BTC net below **$13M** with anchor trimming. Hard downgrade remains `anon-0x8fcc` flips short above `$2M`, or BTC net falls below `$10M`. Keep ETH bearish confidence moderate-high. Keep SOL bearish by notional, but mark count confidence slightly softened. No PM Sunday exception. No HL live trade while notional guard blocks execution.\n\n**Next:** Watch whether BTC anchor creep (`anon-0xecb6`, `anon-0x57dd`) continues enough to reclaim `$15M`, and whether SOL count softening becomes real notional recovery or just dust longs.\n\n## 2026-05-03 11:17 UTC \u2014 [Pillar 4] Range-friendly neutral recovery\n\n**Task:** Refresh P4 alpha after drafting the HL micro-drift paper strategy, checking whether fast-DOWN range drift persisted or mean-reverted.\n\n**Finding:**\n- Both bots are alive (`pm-bot`, `hl-bot`).\n- Rotation pointed to **P4**.\n- Fresh alpha snapshot: `2026-05-03T11:17:20.433887+00:00`.\n- Classifier remains **`range_mean_revert_friendly`**.\n- Transition posture remains **stable**.\n- PM risk remains **low**.\n- Breakout risk remains **neutral",
